---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Jeanine White" description="About Jeanine White Lorem Ipsum">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/at-work.jpg"
					alt="Jeanine White at work with a colleague"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						<a href="">TEK-KONNECT</a> 
					</p>Tek-konnect is a talented web developer who excels in both front-end and back-end development.
					 With a deep understanding of HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and modern frameworks like React or Angular, they create visually appealing and highly functional websites. 
					 On the back-end, they are proficient in server-side languages such as Node.js, Python, or PHP, ensuring robust and scalable web applications.

					<p>
						Tek-konnect is also well-versed in database management, using SQL or NoSQL databases to store and retrieve data efficiently.
						 Their expertise extends to version control systems like Git, allowing for smooth collaboration and code management. 
						 They are continuously learning and adapting to new technologies and best practices in the ever-evolving field of web development.
					</p>
					<p>
						In addition to technical skills, Tek-konnect has a keen eye for design, making sure that user experience
						 (UX) and user interface (UI) principles are integrated into their projects.
						 Their problem-solving abilities and attention to detail make them a valuable asset in any development team.
						  Whether working on a simple website or a complex web application,
						 Tek-konnect brings creativity, dedication, and technical prowess to every project they undertake.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>100%</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>100%</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
